node.text:
Big news! You all know how much I love my air fryer, my NEW cookbook Skinnytaste Air Fryer Dinners: 75 Healthy Recipes for Easy Weeknight Meals is out for pre-order! The book hits shelves Dec 14 but you can pre-order now and be one of the first to get your copy! Filled with 75 dinner recipes to make weeknight meals in the air fryer easier and healthier. Swipe to see some of the photos of the recipes from photographer @aubriepick Each recipe has a photo and nutritional info by @heatherkjonesrd plus helpful icons for gluten-free, vegetarian, dairy-free, etc. 

LINK IN PROFILE TO PRE-ORDER (You can pre-order online on Amazon, Barnes and Noble, Books A Million, and Indiebooks) https://amzn.to/3tgzSCN (Affil link)
#skinnytasteairfryerdinners #skinnytasteairfryerdinnerscookbook

Grilled Chicken Bruschetta is a summer staple in my house! Basically a caprese made with juicy tomatoes, mozzarella, basil, red onion, garlic and balsamic, a delicious weeknight meal!

INGREDIENTS

3 medium vine ripe tomatoes
2 small cloves garlic, minced
1/4 cup chopped red onion
2 tbsp fresh basil leaves
1 tbsp extra virgin oil
1 tbsp balsamic vinegar
kosher salt and pepper 
mozzarella, diced
thin sliced chicken cutlets

Get the full recipe on Skinnytaste! https://www.skinnytaste.com/grilled-chicken-bruschetta/ #dinner #dinnerideas #grilledchicken #chickenbreast #chickenbreastrecipe #skinnytaste #skinnytasterecipe
